---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "@/components/Section.astro";
---

<Layout title="Fajar Maftuh Fadli">
    <Section>
        <h1>Fajar Maftuh Fadli</h1>
        <p>DevOps Engineer · Cloud Architect · Infrastructure Automation</p>
        <p>
            I design, automate, and secure cloud infrastructure that scales —
            from startups to enterprise systems. Specializing in GCP, Terraform,
            monitoring, and reliability engineering.
        </p>
        <button>View Projects</button>
        <button>Download CV</button>
        <button>Contact Me</button>
    </Section>
    <Section>
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
            I'm a DevOps Engineer focused on building reliable, secure, and
            scalable cloud systems. My work lives at the interSection of
            infrastructure automation, observability, and system design. I
            specialize in Google Cloud Platform, infrastructure-as-code, and
            enterprise-scale environments — helping organizations move from
            fragile setups to structured, automated, and resilient
            architectures.
        </p>
        <p>I care about:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc">
            <li>Clean system design</li>
            <li>Least-privilege security</li>
            <li>Cost efficiency</li>
            <li>Reliability over hype</li>
            <li>Automation over manual ops</li>
            <li>Simplicity over complexity</li>
        </ul>
        <q>If it can be automated, it should be automated.</q>
    </Section>
    <Section>
        <h2>Skills & Stack</h2>
        <h3>Cloud</h3>
        <p>
            Google Cloud Platform (GCP) Compute Engine, IAM, BigQuery, Cloud
            Functions, Cloud Storage, Cloud Monitoring, Cloud Logging
        </p>
        <h3>Infrastructure as Code</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Terraform</li>
            <li>Pulumi</li>
            <li>Terragrunt</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>CI/CD</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>GitHub Actions</li>
            <li>Jenkins</li>
            <li>Azure DevOps</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>DevOps</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Linux</li>
            <li>Git</li>
            <li>Docker</li>
            <li>Kubernetes</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Development</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript</li>
            <li>React</li>
            <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
        </ul>
    </Section>
    <Section>
        <h2>Experience</h2>
        <h3>DevOps Engineer — PT FISClouds Innovations</h3>
        <p>Sep 2022 – Present</p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Designed and developed cloud Proof of Concepts (POC) for
                enterprise clients
            </li>
            <li>Built cost-optimized GCP architectures</li>
            <li>Automated infrastructure provisioning using Terraform</li>
            <li>Implemented monitoring, logging, and alerting systems</li>
            <li>Delivered technical documentation (TSD, FSD)</li>
            <li>Supported production environments and troubleshooting</li>
        </ul>
    </Section>
    <Section>
        <h2>Projects / Case Studies</h2>
        <h3>Bank CIMB — GCP Data Platform Automation</h3>
        <h4>Problem:</h4>
        <p>
            Manual IAM management across hundreds of BigQuery datasets created
            security risks and operational overhead.
        </p>
        <h4>Solution:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Built Terraform automation for IAM provisioning</li>
            <li>Implemented least-privilege access model</li>
            <li>Automated dataset & table permissions</li>
            <li>Created usage dashboards in Looker Studio</li>
            <li>Built alerting system for BigQuery usage anomalies</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Impact</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Security hardening</li>
            <li>Zero manual IAM provisioning</li>
            <li>Scalable data governance</li>
            <li>Cost visibility</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Bank Danamon — Enterprise Data Platform</h3>
        <h4>Scope:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>On-prem → Cloud data integration</li>
            <li>Multi-database ETL architecture</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Work done:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Designed ETL pipelines (PostgreSQL, Oracle, MySQL → BigQuery)
            </li>
            <li>Automated GCP infrastructure (VMs, Composer, Data Fusion)</li>
            <li>Centralized logging and monitoring</li>
            <li>
                Built notification system using:
                <ul class="pl-6">
                    <li>Pub/Sub</li>
                    <li>Cloud Functions</li>
                    <li>Secret Manager</li>
                    <li>Telegram & Microsoft Teams integrations</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </Section>
</Layout>
